_source.resolution: Verify that the correct SSL certificates are configured. Check if the certificate authority (CA) is trusted. If using self-signed certificates, ensure they are imported correctly.

_source.resolution: Reduce batch size, clear GPU memory (torch.cuda.empty_cache() for PyTorch), or move to CPU-based inference if necessary. Consider upgrading the GPU.
